OL,3,COwners of airport promise to improve
OL,4,Caccess following fatal hit and run
OL,6,FThe owners of Bournemouth Airport and
OL,7,FBCP Council have promised to improve
OL,8,Faccess to the airport following a
OL,9,Ffatal hit and run.
OL,11,FBilly Lardner, 16, was killed along
OL,12,FParley Lane on the evening of 30 June
OL,13,F2023 by a drink driver.
OL,15,FBilly had just finished work at the
OL,16,Fairport and was on his way to be
OL,17,Fpicked up by his brother at the nearby
OL,18,Fjunction.
