OL,3,COwners of airport promise to improve
OL,4,Caccess following fatal hit and run
OL,6,FHe was hit by a car that was
OL,7,Ftravelling at 80mph, whilst walking
OL,8,Fover a pedestrian crossing.
OL,10,FFollowing the inquest into Billy's
OL,11,Fdeath last year, the Dorset Coroner
OL,12,Fhighlighted the lack of public
OL,13,Ftransport and pedestrian access to the
OL,14,Fairport.
OL,16,FMany passengers are dropped off and
OL,17,Fcollected in the road opposite the
OL,18,Fairport, and then walk in the road
OL,19,Fopposite to and from the terminal.
