OL,3,COwners of airport promise to improve
OL,4,Caccess following fatal hit and run
OL,6,FIn a statement, BCP Council said: "The
OL,7,Fdeath of Billy Lardner was tragic,
OL,8,Fcaused by the dangerous actions of a
OL,9,Fspeeding and intoxicated driver, and
OL,10,Four sympathies remain with Billy's
OL,11,Ffamily and friends.
OL,13,F"We have carefully reviewed the
OL,14,Ffindings of the coroner's report and
OL,15,Fare currently consulting the public on
OL,16,Freducing the speed limit along Parley
OL,17,FLane from 60mph to 40mph.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
