OL,3,COwners of airport promise to improve
OL,4,Caccess following fatal hit and run
OL,6,F"We will continue to work with
OL,7,FBournemouth Airport to provide
OL,8,Fpedestrian access to their site and to
OL,9,Fincrease bus services."
OL,11,FThe Airport has now developed plans
OL,12,Ffor a pedestrian footpath alongside
OL,13,Fthe part of Hurn Court Lane north of
OL,14,FParley Lane.
OL,16,FA development consultation will be
OL,17,Fcarried out before building plans are
OL,18,Ffinalised. The Airport says it's
OL,19,F"optimistic" that the footpath will be
OL,20,Fcompleted this summer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
