OL,6,FTyrone Franklin, aged 25 of Poole, was
OL,7,Fsentenced to 11 years at Bournemouth
OL,8,FCrown Court, after admitting charges
OL,9,Fof causing death by dangerous driving,
OL,10,Ffailing to stop at the scene of an
OL,11,Faccident and driving without valid
OL,12,Finsurance.
